item.title: Entrepreneur paves the way in male-dominated tech industry
item.description: Through innovative thinking, hard work and principled determination, Iranian-American Roya Ansari has led a successful career in Silicon Valley, marked by the founding of her own data companies and a generous commitment to paying it forward. This is Roya’s story.
